Halloween Ghosts Spooktacular Birthday Party Invitation

Top 5! Halloween Ghosts Spooktacular Birthday Party Invitation – Halloween Cards Halloween Ghosts Spooktacular Birthday Party Invitation products with good quality, you can be confident Halloween Ghosts Spooktacular Birthday Party Invitation quality productsModern Halloween-themed birthday invitations for any age! This design features 6 sketch-style ghost illustrations around the edge of the card. Inside the frame of ghosts, there is a modern typography layout to display the event text. "Come & join us for" curves around the top of the birthday boy’s name, written in big capital letters, with "spooktacular birthday party" below. The date and time appear to the left with the address and RSVP details aligned to the left next to them. There is a template message with extra information about a costume party that you can change to suit your needs. This design is black and white, but "Spooktacular" stands out with a pop of orange to give a true Halloween touch! Cards reverse to the same orange with hand-drawn white stripes. To get started customizing these invites, simply click on the "Personalize this template" button and change the placeholder text. If you would like to access the more advanced editing options, select "Click to customize further" and you will be able to edit fonts, colors, placement, and more! Feel free to contact me with any questions, but please note that I can’t modify an existing order! More fall and Halloween birthday party invitations are available in our store! Price:$1.95
